 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt'>定義</span></li>
 <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>ARDS（急性呼吸窘迫症候群）是一臨床症候群，特徵包括：</span></li>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>急性發作</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>的</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>嚴重呼吸困難</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>（severe
       dyspnea of rapid onset）</span></li>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>低血氧</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>症（hypoxemia）</span></li>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>瀰漫性肺部浸潤</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>（diffuse
       pulmonary infiltrates）</span></li>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>導致</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>呼吸衰竭</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>（respiratory
       failure）</span></li>
  </ul>
 </ul>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:5pt;
     margin-bottom:5pt'><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
     font-size:16.0pt'>病因</span></li>
 <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:
      5pt;margin-bottom:5pt'><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
      font-size:14.0pt'>ARDS是因疾病引起的瀰漫性肺損傷所導致，肺損傷可分為：</span></li>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>直接損傷（如pneumonia、aspiration
       of gastric contents、pulmonary contusion、near-drowning、吸入有毒氣體）</span></li>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>間接損傷（如敗血症、嚴重外傷、multiple
       transfusions、drug overdose、胰臟炎、postcardiopulmonary bypass）</span></li>
  </ul>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#C00000'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>Pneumonia和sepsis為最常引起ARDS的原因</span></li>
  </ul>
 </ul>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt'>診斷（Berlin's
     definition）</span></li>
</ul>

